{"tid":1390287,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史係咁話  -  以暴抗暴真勇武？","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:45:24.000Z","uid":2938,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"398b4ad4ac318bbfbeb6bccb82d590edb79df2da","tid":1390287,"uid":2938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"歷史係咁話  -  以暴抗暴真勇武？<br />\n<br />\n歷史上一場運動的書寫向來掌握在勝方手中，中間的過程經當權者渲染，或者套上光環，或者嚴厲譴責。我們回看歷史上的種種反抗運動，從太平天國到法國大革命，在至於印度獨立運動。前人或成功或失敗，如何在勇武與和理非之間選擇，又如何謹記中心信仰？種種經驗總有借鏡之處。站在反抗者與當權者的兩極，究竟什麽叫暴力？如何在反抗暴政時還能保持克制，保護自己和同路人？連場運動過後，人們又何去何從？容我們於今集「以暴抗暴真勇武？」一起探討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-1DUyalf1wY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-1DUyalf1wY&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnSTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=67159fa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-1DUyalf1wY</a>"},{"pid":"922634506ff5af4914e2dec10efdbc0aeecf87dd","tid":1390287,"uid":94819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52d7e9a029fc84316b64e590cff1031dcdb693fb","tid":1390287,"uid":2938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"0396ad577b063f0d4f9984d45ba51debc003d033","tid":1390287,"uid":201031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"今集好好睇<br />\n主持用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be33ee27cf86706ca06d759b5de5e2474e548ba","tid":1390287,"uid":2938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"我唔解鎖"},{"pid":"8eb688cd0f0aa6bc67aa22ef14960a25d3491979","tid":1390287,"uid":2938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"0b68eeeab5a4d4cdc48eaa076d71578f3ebd373b","tid":1390287,"uid":92565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"推呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm